2.def greet(name):
    print ('Hello', name)

greet('Jack')
greet('Jill')
greet('Bob')

Python Flow Control are if,else; for loop; while loop; break and continue and pass.
It has different datatypes such as numbers, list, tuples,string,set and dictionary.


